{"tid":1697452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【呃人又斷正】何君堯昨稱田螺車貼海報被焚　CCTV揭火後貼宣傳品","createTime":"2019-11-07T01:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T01:39:29.000Z","uid":236171,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2cd62da151c9d46fee5f6d299580f25ddd2a1b","tid":1697452,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:08:18.000Z","msg":"其實何妖有幾恨做影帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那01，唔貼 link 了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會新界西候選人何君堯聲稱，昨凌晨有支持者的混凝土田螺車被焚燒，並稱相信縱火原因是該車貼有其宣傳海報，而「遭受迫害」。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》今日取得多條獨家事發片段，可見混凝土田螺車被焚燒一刻，車場內未見貼有何君堯宣傳品，至昨晨何舉行記者會之前，才有3名男子為在場田螺車貼上支持何君堯的海報。<br />\n<br />\n記者今日致電何君堯，對方先稱當日案發前車場內滿是他的海報，之後又稱海報只貼於車頭，其後再改稱案發後因「怕惡勢力」曾撕走海報，到早上才為在場車輛補貼上海報。"},{"pid":"9ec3a888df28e9afabb326cc10311421072c84d9","tid":1697452,"uid":237342,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那01連何妖都踩？<br />\n班藍屍覺得何妖最做到野喎"},{"pid":"0d242af3c587adb6163e0a493f13631dbc5c723d","tid":1697452,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db22da8ea11c5ffab582b5493ea841c60eb3aec","tid":1697452,"uid":185854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T01:18:03.000Z","msg":"真係01黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7288aba6185b30c5743a59ebb8c912d717ae1eb6","tid":1697452,"uid":32221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9ec3a888df28e9afabb326cc10311421072c84d9","tid":1697452,"uid":